February Stock Ashampoo programs (2011/MULTi)

This version features the latest versions, with the latest updates for February 2011 from the developer Ashampoo. The programs are designed to perform multiple tasks: working with the CD / DVD, the optimization of computer virus protection, recovery of hard drives, editing text documents and many others.
